1)->To create a new process by invoking the appropriate system call.
Get the process identifier of the currently running process and its respective parent using system calls and display the same using a C program.

 -->source code.....

#include<stdio.h>
#include<unistd.h>
int main()
{
  printf("Process ID: %d\n", getpid() );
  printf("Parent Process ID: %d\n", getpid() );
  return 0;
}
